_add("quality_score", "Sector Quality Score", "Composite Communication-Services quality score (0-100).", "Weighted: Moat (20), Subscriber/Engagement quality (20), Financial Position/Leverage (15), Capex/Content discipline (10), Dilution/SBC (10), Unit Economics (15), Revenue Predictability (10). >75 elite, <30 weak.", "Weighted sum across 7 axes", "comm_quality")
