_add("content_library_assessment", "Content Library Assessment", "Depth, IP ownership, library breadth and exclusivity.", "Streaming/media defining moat. Disney+Marvel+Pixar, Netflix originals, WBD library — inversely related to needed content investment.", "Derived from content spend + IP disclosures", "comm_quality")
